    "updated_at": "2016-05-27T04:16:38Z",
    "body": "I was able to reproduce this and @kevinsawicki and I looked into some today but aren't sure the best fix.\n\nIt's just a problem on OS X and how the hidden title bar is only sort-of-kind-of hidden. For instance hover events still work in this area but the cursor will change back to default. \n\nThere are some different ways to remove/hide this title bar and maybe someone else has some pointers on which is the best route?\n"
  },
